title: Gulf markets fall among uncertainty - Al Jazeera 5th Oct 2008
description:
Gulf markets fall among uncertainty - 5 Oct 08


Markets in the Middle East have closed deep in the red. 

They had been spared the pain over the last five days because they were closed for Eid holidays. But no respite for them today. 

Al Jazeera&#039;s Hashem Ahelbarra reports from Doha, Qatar.
